{"word":"H6970 - קֹועַ - Qôwaʻ - ko'-ah - Koa","slug":"H6970","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קֹועַ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Qôwaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ko'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Koa"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>קוע</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>qôa‛</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>ko'-ah</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Koa = \"he-camel\" <ol><li>a territory in Mesopotamia, east of the Tigris, on border of Elam and Media</li></ol> <p />Origin: probably from <a href=\"#/H6972\">H6972</a> in the original sense of cutting off <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Location "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3351\">H3351</a>, <a href=\"#/H3356\">H3356</a>, <a href=\"#/H3359\">H3359</a>, <a href=\"#/H3360\">H3360</a>, <a href=\"#/H3361\">H3361</a>, <a href=\"#/H4725\">H4725</a>, <a href=\"#/H6965\">H6965</a>, <a href=\"#/H6967\">H6967</a>, <a href=\"#/H6968\">H6968</a>, <a href=\"#/H6971\">H6971</a>, <a href=\"#/H7009\">H7009</a>, <a href=\"#/H7012\">H7012</a>, <a href=\"#/H7054\">H7054</a>, <a href=\"#/H7056\">H7056</a>, <a href=\"#/H8617\">H8617</a>, <a href=\"#/H8618\">H8618</a>"}]}